{"tid":1386840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急 要人] 45位義士聽日提堂 要去聲援","createTime":"2019-07-30T12:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T16:30:05.000Z","uid":213862,"like":174,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"9f6625786959dbf7a696b129afda8f3289158903","tid":1386840,"uid":213862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:03:49.000Z","msg":"如果判刑會引起社會進一步混亂 佢地唔敢重判<br />\n我地下一代被人扼殺 一定要去呀<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">淨係知道聽日朝早會喺東區法院提堂</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果有任何時間上嘅update 請留言告知<br />\n<br />\n我知咁樣去聲援未必有咩效果<br />\n但係到呢刻 我真係唔知仲可以點<br />\n心情好憤怒 好撚嬲<br />\n<br />\n身為學生嘅我 依家放緊暑假 冇藉口唔去<br />\n我一個人都會出去聲援<br />\n但係我知道聽日點都會見到同行嘅你地去聲援<br />\n希望各位巴絲聽日得閒一齊去東區法院聲援<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位手足將呢個訊息share出去<br />\nshare到你嘅fb ig whatsapp snapchat 等等<br />\n唔係個個都睇連登<br />\n<br />\n感謝你地 <br />\n一定要救曬每一個<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">釋放義士 撤銷控罪</span></strong>"},{"pid":"0e6e439d187113955b8d76f2a808cc84b4d92467","tid":1386840,"uid":1315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:03:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e3cc40198fdeba3c46f469da5675edb3ef5c533","tid":1386840,"uid":213862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:03:56.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"6820327ac3a43b815a349699c0112636139c9299","tid":1386840,"uid":213862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:04:06.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"91d07097fad78df0e8196c94f5a3dae1793f9fd3","tid":1386840,"uid":213862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:04:17.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"05b18088b6783c8d4cede9884fb7a4f68dab56d0","tid":1386840,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:04:24.000Z","msg":"8.5全民罷工 今次到我哋和理非主場 唔好比個垃圾港共政權睇死我地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386454</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" cl